Package graph.edge

Interface WeightedEdge<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

Type Parameters:
T - A generic that extends Comparable
All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<WeightedEdge<T>>
All Known Implementing Classes:
SimpleWeightedEdge
public interface WeightedEdge<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Comparable<WeightedEdge<T>>
An interface that provides the functionality of getting the weight of an edge, getting the source and getting its destination. The weight of this edge is a generic type that must be (Comparable). The source and destionations of the edge must be int.
